"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-02-27-paris-olympics-security-plans-stolen-train\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS,\\u00a0France\\u00a0(AFP)- A bag containing a computer and two USB memory sticks holding police security plans for the Paris Olympic Games was stolen on Monday evening from a train at the capital's Gare du Nord station, police sources said Tuesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9973032413496552, \"rank\": 0.001818327329636057, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 57, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.918244806805253, \"rank\": 0.08902977239311986, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bag belonged to an engineer from Paris City Hall, the police said, confirming a report by BFM television, adding that he had put the bag in the luggage compartment above his seat.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 338, \"end\": 341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 0.7736235665918377, \"rank\": 0.29063548026758373, \"text\": \"BFM\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As his train was delayed, he decided to change trains at which point he discovered the theft.\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The engineer said his work computer and two USB sticks contained sensitive data, in particular the municipal police's plans for securing the Olympics.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 568, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.918244806805253, \"rank\": 0.08902977239311986, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An investigation is being conducted by the regional transport police.\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris City Hall was not able to immediately comment when contacted by AFP.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999991163122, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris City Hall\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f4tel_de_Ville,_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Federal_Police\", \"score\": 0.9690830356089644, \"rank\": 0.03188473400654829, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Federal_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Federal_Police\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two thousand municipal police officers will be deployed during the Games, with a total of around 35,000 security forces expected to be on duty each day for the Olympics that start on July 26.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}]}"